<title>
O/D Off Switch Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove console box. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B9806012"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect select lever connector.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check for continuity between terminals “3” and “8” of select lever connector (1).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified, replace select lever assembly.
</ptxt>
